      "personalDetails": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Both</p>\n<p><strong>Aliases:</strong> Mr. Castaigne; Henri Castaigne</p>\n<h2>Player Description</h2>\n<p>Tiny white-haired man in antiquated clothes, shuffling through papers and old photos.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<h2>Handler Notes</h2>\n<p>Self-styled heir and trapped Night World resident; obsessed with kingship, hidden genealogies, and his Soul Bottle.</p>\n<h3>Linked Locations</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Night Floors</li>\n<li>Macallistar Building</li>\n<li>Broadalbin</li>\n<li>Bookshop</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Linked Clues</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>lineage pages</li>\n<li>crown delusion</li>\n<li>“Superintendent” lead</li>\n<li>cousin reference to Hildred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Recurring Status:</strong> OP1</p>\n<p><strong>Source Pages:</strong> IL pp. 102-104, 115</p>\n</section>",
